## Topics Already Covered (banter only)

These are the explicit banter topics this party has already used. **Do not pick a topic that is the same theme as any of these — even loosely related counts as repetition.** "Complaining about the cold" and "remarking on the weather" are the same theme; "ribbing about a missed arrow" and "ribbing about clumsy footwork" are the same theme.

